columns.name: DOMAIN_NAME
columns.description: Database domain where this data is stored.

columns.name: INSERT_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the user inserting the data.

columns.name: INSERT_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of data insert.

columns.name: UPDATE_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the user updating the data.

columns.name: UPDATE_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of the most recent data update.

columns.name: PROJECT_GID
columns.description: The GID of the machine learning project.

columns.name: SCENARIO_GID
columns.description: The GID of the machine learning scenario.

columns.name: SHIPMENT_GID
columns.description: The GID of the shipment.

columns.name: MODEL_TYPE
columns.description: The type of the machine learning model for the scenario. 'A' denotes active model and 'B' denotes beta model.

columns.name: WORKFLOW_ID
columns.description: The workflow request ID used by the machine learning scenario.

columns.name: LEARNING_ID
columns.description: The learning request ID used by the machine learning scenario.

columns.name: TRAINING_MODEL_ID
columns.description: The model ID used by the machine learning scenario.

columns.name: SCORING_RESPONSE_ID
columns.description: The scoring response ID used by the perform scoring action.

columns.name: SCORING_REQUEST_STATUS
columns.description: The status of the scoring request for the scenario.

columns.name: ACCURACY
columns.description: The accuracy of the Machine learning scenario scoring.

columns.name: FORECAST
columns.description: The details of the learning results stored in json format.

columns.name: TARGET_VALUE
columns.description: Denotes the predicted value.

columns.name: PREDICTION_INTERVAL_LOW
columns.description: Denotes the lower range number of the prediction interval which is used to quantify the uncertainities in prediction result.

columns.name: PREDICTION_INTERVAL_HIGH
columns.description: Denotes the higher range value of the prediction interval which is used to quantify the uncertainities in prediction result.

columns.name: I_TRANSACTION_NO
columns.description: The I_TRANSACTION_NO column specifies the transaction to which this log message pertains.

columns.name: I_REC_NO
columns.description: The record number primary key identifier for the tracking event specified.

columns.name: LANE
columns.description: The lane used by the shipment

columns.name: GEO_HASH_CODE
columns.description: A Geohash code is a unique identifier of a specific region on the Earth.

columns.name: LANE_ACCURACY
columns.description: The accuracy of the scoring on a machine learning scenario lane.

columns.name: GEO_HASH_LANE_ACCURACY
columns.description: The accuracy of the scoring on a machine learning scenario geohash lane.
